    "body": "I narrowed down the problem slightly: rustdoc spawns a ton of pandoc threads (over 20); each one uses 12 MB of memory and that causes my machine to thrash (apparently 4 GB of physical RAM isn't enough...)\n\nPerhaps there should be some limit on the number of live threads rustdoc can spawn at once.\n",
